    "Various challenges require careful planning, and various models and algorithms have been devised to address them effectively.",
    "Time constraints in MS-RCPSPWhile our primary objective for this review is to examine the MS-RCPSP in the context of resource constraints, numerous studies have also investigated additional constraints, including time constraints, tardiness objectives, and other time-related considerations.",
